Uses Text Search (New) with rectangle locationRestriction:
```typescript
async function searchArea(bounds: LatLngBounds, query?: string) {
  return providerGateway.textSearch({
    textQuery: query || 'restaurant',
    locationRestriction: {
      rectangle: {
        low: { latitude: bounds.south, longitude: bounds.west },
        high: { latitude: bounds.north, longitude: bounds.east },
